data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful city of Port Saint Lucie! This delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage single-family home with a pool combines comfort and convenience flawlessly.It's open floor plan strikes a perfect balance of style and functionality.The kitchen, completely revamped, showcases stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a generous island boasting ample cabinet space. Plus, there's a large window that overlooks the pool, infusing the space with natural light and a delightful view.The master bedroom features tray ceilings, a roomy walk-in closet, and a renovated master bathroom that includes a spacious walk-in shower with dual shower heads, a separate and tranquil Roman tub, and tasteful finishes throughout the ensuite. With a thoughtfully designed split floor plan, this home guarantees privacy for every family member or visiting guest. The newer roof, installed in 2022, provides peace of mind.

The outdoor living space is a true gem. Step through the sliding doors and enter your own private paradise. The screened-in pool and spacious lanai create the ideal setting for year-round entertainment and relaxation. The upgraded cabana bath offers both convenience and style. The fully fenced backyard provides ample space for children and pets to play freely. 

Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity. Schedule a viewing today and immerse yourself in the charm and beauty this remarkable property has to offer. Make it your forever home!
